Package: AnnDatR
Title: AnnDatR: A native R6 Data Container for transcriptomics data analysis and visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emilio", "Skarwan", , "emilio.skarwan@scilifelab.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: AnnDatR provides an efficient, R-native implementation of AnnData data structure, widely used in the Python Scanpy ecosystem. Built on the R6 object system, it allows researchers to store, manage, process and visualize transcriptomics datasets. It includes essential functionality for data preprocessing, quality control, dimensionality reduction (PCA, UMAP), gene specificity analysis (HPA classification, Tau score), and visualization.
